name: The Magical Item #15: Nar: The Ramen Temple
description: After learning the secret of Jaru, Dino asked the Jaru Fairy to take him to his hometown, the 15th Magical Location. There are two ways to enter this temple: the first is to be part of the Jaru Family and the second is to win the food battle against Fejane, the protector of the city. Each bite triggers the pain that the members of the Jaru family endured during their life. The first to drop the Chopsword loses the battle. The competition begins, Dino sits in front of the giant Ramen, and Fejane orders the flow of food to commence. Dino is determined to win this challenge and would do everything to prove to his friend his love and loyalty. Unlocking this portal will increase your Appetite by 790 MPs.
